        <h4 class="font-bold text-stone-800 mb-2">How this works</h4>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          The system analyzes the NPK readings to identify the 'limiting nutrient' (the one in shortest supply). 
          It then queries the internal database for organic amendments highest in that specific nutrient 
