1.  **NPK Sensor Node:** Reads RS485 Modbus data.
2.  **Tank & Motor Controller:** Reads analog sensors (Gas, pH), DHT (Temp/Hum), and controls Relays/Motors via L298N drivers.

Here is the complete C++ / Arduino code for both devices.

